WEBVTT

00:00:00.437 --> 00:00:02.246
Track 08.06

00:00:03.957 --> 00:00:06.211
Angela: I went to the beach last week.

00:00:06.497 --> 00:00:07.750
It was great.

00:00:07.973 --> 00:00:11.481
Sol: Oh, let’s go to the beach together some time!

00:00:11.623 --> 00:00:13.687
Angela: That’s a lovely idea.

00:00:13.806 --> 00:00:15.607
Sol: We could go this weekend.

00:00:16.037 --> 00:00:17.187
Angela: I’m sorry,

00:00:17.323 --> 00:00:19.790
I’m busy with my family this weekend.

00:00:19.790 --> 00:00:22.899
Sol: OK. Shall we go next Saturday?

00:00:23.280 --> 00:00:25.105
Angela: I can’t go on Saturday,

00:00:25.130 --> 00:00:27.212
but I’m free on Sunday.

00:00:27.237 --> 00:00:29.086
I can go on Sunday.

00:00:29.143 --> 00:00:31.341
Sol:  OK, Sunday. Good.

00:00:31.563 --> 00:00:32.389
Angela: Great!